---
import Head from '../../components/Head.astro';
import '../../styles/fonts.css';
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<Head
			title="Pascale Richard — Ensemble pour NY 2026"
			description="Candidate Renaissance pour les Français de New York, New Jersey et Connecticut. Journaliste, élue, engagée depuis 2016."
			path="/v/4"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- ═══ DARK HERO ═══ -->
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-border-top"></div>
			<nav>
				<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_logo-complet_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="nav-logo" />
			</nav>

			<div class="hero-inner">
				<div class="ornament">✦</div>
				<div class="portrait-wrapper">
					<img src="/assets/images/pascale.jpg" alt="Pascale Richard" class="portrait" />
				</div>
				<h1>Pascale Richard</h1>
				<p class="role">Conseillère des Français de l'étranger</p>
				<div class="geo">
					<span>New York</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>New Jersey</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>Connecticut</span>
				</div>

				<div class="divider"><span class="divider-diamond">◆</span></div>

				<p class="quote">« Le plus satisfaisant est d'aider mes concitoyens. Conseiller des Français de l'étranger est une fonction méconnue, mais les conseillers font un travail important. »</p>

				<ul class="facts">
					<li><strong>25+ ans</strong> à New York</li>
					<li><strong>Engagée</strong> depuis 2016</li>
					<li><strong>Élue</strong> en 2021</li>
					<li><strong>Suppléante</strong> de R. Lescure</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
				<div class="ornament bottom">✦</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-border-bottom"></div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ PRIORITIES ═══ -->
		<section class="priorities">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
					<p class="section-label">Engagements</p>
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
				</div>
				<h2>Trois priorités pour notre communauté</h2>
				<div class="priority-grid">
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">— 01 —</div>
						<h3>Solidarité</h3>
						<div class="card-rule"></div>
						<p>Accompagner les Français en difficulté aux États-Unis — personnes âgées isolées, malades, familles touchées par la vie chère. Orienter chacun vers les bons interlocuteurs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">— 02 —</div>
						<h3>Lien & événements</h3>
						<div class="card-rule"></div>
						<p>Soutenir les associations et événements qui créent du lien — de Bastille Day aux salons de l'éducation bilingue — et rassembler les Français de toute la circonscription.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">— 03 —</div>
						<h3>Services numériques</h3>
						<div class="card-rule"></div>
						<p>Accompagner la mise en place de France Consulaire et le vote par Internet. Tenir les Français informés, simplifier les démarches administratives à distance.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ QUOTE BAND ═══ -->
		<section class="quote-band">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="quote-ornament">❧</div>
				<blockquote>
					« Il y a une résilience des gens qui n'attendent pas tout de leur gouvernement. C'est notre relation à l'État qui doit évoluer. »
				</blockquote>
				<div class="quote-ornament flipped">❧</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ TIMELINE ═══ -->
		<section class="parcours">
			<div class="container narrow">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
					<p class="section-label">Parcours</p>
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
				</div>
				<h2>D'une carrière dans les médias à l'engagement politique</h2>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">Années 2000</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Installation à New York</h4>
							<p>Carrière de journaliste. Rédactrice en chef de France Amérique. Directrice des événements culturels au Lycée Français de New York.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2016</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Engagement avec En Marche</h4>
							<p>S'engage dès la première heure avec le mouvement d'Emmanuel Macron. Campagne aux côtés de Roland Lescure pour l'Amérique du Nord.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2017</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Suppléante du député Lescure</h4>
							<p>Suppléante pendant la première mandature du député de la 1ère circonscription des Français établis hors de France.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2021</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Élue conseillère des Français de l'étranger</h4>
							<p>Tête de liste En Marche pour NY, NJ, CT et les Bermudes. Élue à l'Assemblée des Français de l'étranger, commission développement durable.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item current">
						<span class="tl-year">2026</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Candidate aux législatives</h4>
							<p>Candidate Renaissance aux élections législatives pour représenter les Français de la circonscription tri-state.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ EVENTS ═══ -->
		<section class="events">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
					<p class="section-label">Événements</p>
					<span class="section-rule"></span>
				</div>
				<h2>Rencontrons-nous</h2>
				<div class="events-placeholder">
					<p class="coming-soon">À venir</p>
					<p class="events-sub">Le calendrier des événements et rencontres sera bientôt disponible. Suivez-nous sur Instagram pour rester informés.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ CTA BOTTOM ═══ -->
		<section class="cta-bottom">
			<div class="cta-top-rule"></div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="ornament">✦</div>
				<h2>Rejoignez le mouvement</h2>
				<p class="cta-sub">Ensemble, construisons l'avenir de notre communauté française aux États-Unis.</p>
				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost-light">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<div class="footer-rule"></div>
			<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_monogramme_marine.png" alt="Renaissance" class="footer-logo" />
			<p>&copy; 2026 Pascale Richard — Ensemble pour NY 2026</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
	   CARTE FRANÇAISE — Classic Parisian menu aesthetic
	   Tricolore palette: navy, white, red.
	   Gold ornaments, elegant rules & dividers.
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */

	:root {
		--navy: #002395;
		--navy-deep: #001A6E;
		--red: #ED2939;
		--red-dark: #C4212F;
		--gold: #C9A84C;
		--gold-light: #D4B96A;
		--white: #FFFFFF;
		--off-white: #F7F8FC;
		--light: #EEF0F8;
		--ink: #1A1A2E;
		--muted: #5C5C72;
		--border: #D8DAE6;
		--rule: #B8BBCF;
	}

	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

	html {
		font-family: 'Maax', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
		color: var(--ink);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	body {
		background: var(--off-white);
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.container.narrow {
		max-width: 720px;
	}

	/* ─── ORNAMENTS ─── */
	.ornament {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--red);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.5em;
		opacity: 0.5;
	}

	.ornament.bottom {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	/* ─── HERO ─── */
	.hero {
		background: var(--navy-deep);
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
	}

	.hero-border-top,
	.hero-border-bottom {
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			var(--navy) 0%,
			var(--navy) 33%,
			var(--white) 33%,
			var(--white) 66%,
			var(--red) 66%,
			var(--red) 100%
		);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	nav {
		padding: 2rem 2rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		height: 22px;
		opacity: 0.65;
	}

	.hero-inner {
		max-width: 660px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem 2.5rem;
	}

	.portrait-wrapper {
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.portrait {
		width: 136px;
		height: 136px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		border: 3px solid var(--white);
		box-shadow:
			0 0 0 4px var(--red),
			0 0 0 8px rgba(237, 41, 57, 0.15);
		transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
		cursor: pointer;
		animation: jig 10s ease-in-out 3s infinite;
	}

	.portrait:hover {
		transform: scale(1.08) rotate(4deg);
		animation: none;
	}

	@keyframes jig {
		0%, 93% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
		94% { transform: rotate(-4deg) scale(1.04); }
		95.5% { transform: rotate(4deg) scale(1.06); }
		97% { transform: rotate(-3deg) scale(1.04); }
		98.5% { transform: rotate(2deg) scale(1.02); }
		99.5% { transform: rotate(-1deg) scale(1.01); }
		100% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		color: var(--white);
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.role {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.geo {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.dot {
		width: 4px;
		height: 4px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--red);
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.divider {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
		max-width: 300px;
	}

	.divider::before,
	.divider::after {
		content: '';
		flex: 1;
		height: 1px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			transparent,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
			transparent
		);
	}

	.divider-diamond {
		color: var(--red);
		font-size: 0.625rem;
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.hero .quote {
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 520px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.facts {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.facts li {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.facts strong {
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.hero .buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	/* ─── BUTTONS (elegant, understated) ─── */
	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
		background: var(--red);
		color: var(--white);
		border: 1px solid var(--red);
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.cta:hover {
		background: var(--red-dark);
		border-color: var(--red-dark);
	}

	.cta.ghost {
		background: transparent;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.cta.ghost:hover {
		border-color: var(--white);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta.ghost-light {
		background: transparent;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.cta.ghost-light:hover {
		border-color: var(--white);
		color: var(--white);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	/* ─── SECTION HEADERS (rule — label — rule) ─── */
	.section-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
	}

	.section-rule {
		flex: 1;
		max-width: 120px;
		height: 1px;
		background: var(--rule);
	}

	.section-label {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--red);
		text-align: center;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	/* ─── PRIORITIES ─── */
	.priorities {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--off-white);
	}

	.priorities h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--navy);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.priority-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.priority-card {
		background: var(--white);
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
	}

	.priority-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -1px;
		left: 20%;
		right: 20%;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--navy), var(--red));
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.card-number {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--red);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
	}

	.priority-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--navy);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.card-rule {
		width: 40px;
		height: 1px;
		background: var(--rule);
		margin: 0 auto 1rem;
	}

	.priority-card p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	/* ─── QUOTE BAND ─── */
	.quote-band {
		background: var(--red);
		padding: 4.5rem 0;
		position: relative;
	}

	.quote-band::before,
	.quote-band::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 10%;
		right: 10%;
		height: 1px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			transparent,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25),
			transparent
		);
	}

	.quote-band::before { top: 1.5rem; }
	.quote-band::after { bottom: 1.5rem; }

	.quote-ornament {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--white);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		opacity: 0.4;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.quote-ornament.flipped {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		transform: scaleX(-1);
	}

	.quote-band blockquote {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	/* ─── TIMELINE ─── */
	.parcours {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--light);
	}

	.parcours h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--navy);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 4rem;
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.625rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		bottom: 0.375rem;
		width: 1px;
		background: var(--rule);
	}

	.tl-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 2.75rem;
	}

	.tl-item:last-child {
		padding-bottom: 0;
	}

	.tl-item::before {
		content: '◆';
		position: absolute;
		left: -4rem;
		top: 0.125rem;
		font-size: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gold);
		transform: translateX(calc(0.625rem - 50% + 0.5px));
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.tl-item.current::before {
		content: '◆';
		color: var(--red);
		font-size: 0.625rem;
	}

	.tl-year {
		display: inline-block;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--navy);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
		padding-bottom: 0.125rem;
	}

	.tl-item.current .tl-year {
		color: var(--red);
		border-color: var(--red);
	}

	.tl-content h4 {
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		color: var(--navy);
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.tl-content p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	/* ─── EVENTS ─── */
	.events {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--off-white);
	}

	.events h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--navy);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.events-placeholder {
		text-align: center;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		max-width: 520px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		background: var(--white);
		position: relative;
	}

	.events-placeholder::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: -1px;
		left: 25%;
		right: 25%;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--navy), var(--red));
		opacity: 0.5;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--navy);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.events-sub {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: var(--muted);
		max-width: 380px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* ─── CTA BOTTOM ─── */
	.cta-bottom {
		background: var(--navy-deep);
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--white);
		position: relative;
	}

	.cta-top-rule {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(
